%% UC-13 quote comparison — gRPC Quote Engine call sequence.  Render at https://mermaid.live
sequenceDiagram
    actor C as Customer
    participant API as PrintHub.Api
    participant DB as SQL Server
    participant QE as QuoteEngine (gRPC)

    C->>API: POST /api/quotes/compare (items, sortBy)
    API->>DB: load service types + eligible shops<br/>(rate cards, price rules, machines)
    loop for each eligible shop
        API->>QE: Estimate(items + shop pricing rules)  [gRPC/h2c]
        QE->>QE: select PricingStrategy per item, apply rules
        QE-->>API: subtotal, estimatedMinutes, breakdown
    end
    alt Quote Engine unavailable
        API->>API: in-process indicative price (IsIndicative = true)
    end
    API->>DB: persist one Quote per shop (24h expiry + breakdown)
    API-->>C: ranked comparison (price / time / rating)
